662 REM ** ANIMATION COUNTER (ALWAYS 1)
663 POKE 37922,1
664 REM ** ANIMATE SPRITE 0? (1=YES)
665 POKE 37923,0

666 REM ** MOVEMENT TIMER (NUMBER OF INTERRUPTS BETWEEN MOVES [1=FASTEST])

