669 POKE 37936,1
670 REM ** SPRITE 0 BOUNCE OFF SPRITES? (1=YES)
671 POKE 37940,1
672 REM ** SPRITE 0 BOUNCE OFF FOREGROUND? (1=YES)
673 POKE 37941,0

